defaultApproximately 75 helicopters serve the UKCS for offshore commercial transfer purposes with three main operators: Bond; Bristow; and CHC, collectively operating upwards of 50,000 flights a year. There are two key manufacturers providing helicopters to the i
defaultndustry; Eurocopter and Sikorsky. 
default&#xa0;
default2.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe Eurocopter Super Puma AS332 L type, AS332 L1 type, AS332 L2 type and EC225 type provide approximately 50 per cent of the service provision.  The remaining 50 per cent are Sikorsky S-92 type helicopters. 
