default&#xa0;default4.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultUnite strongly believes the issues highlighted by 
defaultthe workers and the support for the four key demands emphasise 
defaultthe 
defaultlegitimate and genuine concerns among the workforce regarding 
defaultthe safety of 
defaulthelicopter transfers.  Both government and the wider industry have an obligation to address these concerns. 
default&#xa0;default4.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn 
defaultthe same vein, there should be no surprise in either the industry or in government to the responses received via our consultation 
defaultas 
defaultthese concerns have been growing and exacerbated with each major incident. 
defaultThe problem is further compounded when workers l
defaultook at their Norwegian counterparts and compare the respective safety records. 
default&#xa0;default4.4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe reality is that helicopter transfers are the most efficient, effective and in all likelihood, the safest means of commercial transfer to and from 
defaultoffshore installations. H
defaultowever, that does not mean that changes to improve these transfers ca
defaultnnot be undertaken immediately.
default&#xa0;default4.5.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe oil and gas industry is our growth sector for the next thirty years but it is also at a crossroads as we move into what the industry refers to as the next phase of the UKCS. This is emphasised in the recently published Wood Review Interim Report, which
default has recommended the fast-tracking of measures aimed at maximising the economic benefit of the remaining UK offshore capacity. 
default&#xa0;default4.6.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHowever, while the industry and government speed are at pains to maximise the remaining profits of the UKCS, this pursuit 
defaultmust 
defaultbe matched by an improved and robust health and safety agenda to protect the industry’s most important asset – its people. 
default&#xa0;default4.7.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs a result, Unite urges the committee to take on board these initial findings from our Back Home Safe Campaign as a highly represe
defaultntative sample of opinion from across the UK oil and gas workforce and help to address these clear concerns
default with offshore helicopter safety with the utmost haste. 
